## Development Setup

### Local Development

```bash
# Setup virtual environment and install dependencies
uv sync

# Install pre-commit hooks
pre-commit install --install-hooks

# Make the Claude worklog hook executable
chmod +x .claude/hooks/pre-commit

```

#### Agent Workflow

```
work in Claude Code
  → session file auto-written to .claude/sessions/YY-MM-DD-<slug>.md
git commit
  → pre-commit hook detects new/modified session files
  → calls Claude to summarise into .claude/CHANGELOG.md
  → stages the updated changelog automatically

(when ready to release)
/version-increment patch|minor|major
  → consolidates .claude/CHANGELOG.md into root CHANGELOG.md
  → bumps version in pyproject.toml
  → archives the session log
```


### Using VS Code DevContainer

1. Open project folder in VS Code
2. Install the "Remote - Containers" extension
3. Click "Reopen in Container" or run the "Remote-Containers: Reopen in Container" command
